title: Enjoy Your Coffee on the Patio of a Beautiful 2 Bedroom Apartment HOME
posting_body: ['Your adventure starts here-welcome to The Markham apartments in Cupertino.', 'CALL:', 'show contact info', 'xxxx', 'From $4,351', '.', '2 Bed 2 Bath .', '1092 Sq.Ft', '* Unit 19D - Available 08/13/22', '* Unit 19F - Available 08/27/22', 'Markham Apartments', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Address:', '20800 Homestead Road Cupertino, CA 95014', 'DESCRIPTION', 'The search for your next residence is done with this wonderful two-bedroom, two-bathroom home at The Markham Apartments.', 'This residence presents granite counters in the cooking area.', 'In addition, the all-electric kitchen offers a stainless steel appliance package to assist in making home-cooked meals.', 'A walk-in closet in each bedroom is a prime example of the available storage options.', 'The home also includes a washer and dryer for extra convenience.', 'The private deck even enables you to enjoy the sweeping outdoor views.', 'By becoming a neighbor of this pet-friendly neighborhood, you’ll have exclusive access to the topnotch amenities such as a saltwater pool, a hydrotherapy spa, and a twenty-four-hour fitness center.', 'The Markham offers an on-site electric vehicle charging station, as well as additional storage.', 'For current terms, pricing, and availability, call or email now.', 'FLOORPLAN SPECIALS', '2 Weeks Free on Select Apartments', 'LEASE\u2002\u2002TERMS', 'Variable', 'OFFICE\u2002 \u2002HOURS', 'Monday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Tuesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Wednesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Thursday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Friday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Saturday', '9:00am to 5:00pm', 'Sunday', '9:00am to 5:00pm', 'CALL US TODAY!', 'show contact info', 'xxxx', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'DISCLAIMER:', 'Call for details: pricing/availability subject to change at any time.']
